						               													<description>HI! I am the Pig and I am HAPPY near the Farm and near the Water. If I stop on other places... I become SAD! When Happy I can draw the YELLOW HAPPY NUMBERS, and when Sad I can draw the PURPLE SAD NUMBERS!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;MOOO! I am the Cow and I am HAPPY near the Farm and near the Grass: On these places I can draw THREE HAPPY NUMBERS and if i draw a &amp;quot;+&amp;quot;, then I can sum them! With 5 + 4, I can move up to 9 squares!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Who will be an HAPPY ANIMAL?&amp;#10;Who will arrive first? Maybe someone will stop on a square to stay happy and draw the HAPPY NUMBERS, higher than the SAD NUMBERS! &amp;#10;The choice is yours: always run till the last step or stay happy and win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HAPPYANIMALS is a COMPLETE GAME&amp;#10;for 2-18 players, 5 years and up. Contents:&amp;#10;- 18 Cards with the characteristics of all Animals&amp;#10;- 18 Counters of the Animals, The Happy Numbers and the Sad Numbers&amp;#10;- 1 Board representing the race map with the Farm, the Woods, the Grass, the Water...&amp;#10;- 1 Rule sheet easy (draw and move) and one with addictions, subtractions, multiplications and divisions.&amp;#10;- And... 2 wooden PUSH PUPPETS!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All the 18 wooden push puppets are available: &amp;#10;Pig, Cow, Lion, Donkey, Elephant, Dog, Cat, Giraffe, Gazzelle, Husky, Leopard, Green Dog, Bear, Sheep, Monkey, Bamby, Horse, Zebra.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Push puppets are wonderful handmade and hand-painted animals that when &amp;quot;Happy&amp;quot; stands on their base, when &amp;quot;Sad&amp;quot; flop on their legs!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HAPPYANIMALS will be premiered as prototype at EssenFair 06, Stand SilToys booth number 9-19 and at stand Angelo Porazzi Games booth number 9-28.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
